```

### YapÄ±landÄ±rma

#### Ortam DeÄŸiÅŸkenleri

```bash
# API anahtarlarÄ±
export OPENAI_API_KEY="your-openai-key"
export ANTHROPIC_API_KEY="your-anthropic-key"
export COHERE_API_KEY="your-cohere-key"

# Ollama yapÄ±landÄ±rmasÄ±
